35
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:48,110
That is not a joke.

36
00:01:48,110 --> 00:01:50,560
The good news is, he seems to be recovering.

37
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:54,160
Meanwhile a second US case has been confirmed
in Chicago.

38
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,820
I hope Chicago has robots, too.

39
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:58,020
