rally.

44
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:14,420
It was called Universal Siege Against Communism.

45
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:18,790
And it was to call on other countries to sanction
Hong Kong officials.

46
00:02:18,790 --> 00:02:20,340
These people held up signs that say

47
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:22,840
Heaven Destroys the Chinese Commuinst Party

48
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:27,040
